						               													<description>From the website:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;5150: Urban Renewal is our Sci-Fi RPG. Players adventure in and around New Hope City gaining Fame and Fortune while increasing their abilities. NHC is a complete Blade Runnereque urban environment inhabited by over 50 professions, with humans and aliens alike.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game includes a low bookkeeping complete campaign system to link your adventures and track your progress. Urban Renewal generates your adventures with no two ever being the same!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Urban Renewal is playable solo, cooperatively and competitively, head to head and playable with any figures in any scale&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Urban Renewal is the core rules for a long line of supplements to follow, starting with our first, New Hope City PI.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A sandbox style game, play a one-off standard miniatures game with your opponent on one side of a city block as a group of gangers and yours on the other as the police and have at! (Or step things up and include cybernetics and &amp;quot;Cyndees&amp;quot; and smuggled Star Army weapons to add to the carnage)  Last man standing wins!Add Attributes and skills to make the game more RPG-like, letting your figures advance between games, adding more goals like finding lost technology, raiding corporate headquarters or simply going gambling for an evening and making it out of the casino alive!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Several pre-made scenarios are included in the book allowing you to customize your games to the complexity you desire.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use whatever miniatures you have around!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you liked 5150:Star Army, this merely takes that world and narrows the focus down to 1 figure and one city.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
